      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;publicly-reported-vulnerabilities&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Publicly Reported Vulnerabilities&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#publicly-reported-vulnerabilities&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2023-32402-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT213762&#34;&gt;CVE-2023-32402 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2023-32402-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing web content may disclose sensitive information&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: An out-of-bounds read in WebKit was addressed with improved input validation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2023-32423-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT213762&#34;&gt;CVE-2023-32423 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2023-32423-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing web content may disclose sensitive information&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: A buffer overflow issue was addressed with improved memory handling.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2025-31217-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/122404&#34;&gt;CVE-2025-31217 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2025-31217-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to an unexpected process crash&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: The issue was addressed with improved input validation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2025-43216-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/124147&#34;&gt;CVE-2025-43216 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2025-43216-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to an unexpected process crash&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: A use-after-free issue was addressed with improved memory management.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2025-43368-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/125108&#34;&gt;CVE-2025-43368 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2025-43368-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to an unexpected Safari crash&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: A use-after-free issue was addressed with improved memory management.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;cve-2025-43419-webkit&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://support.apple.com/en-us/125113&#34;&gt;CVE-2025-43419 (WebKit)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cve-2025-43419-webkit&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Processing maliciously crafted web content may lead to memory corruption&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: The issue was addressed with improved memory handling.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;heading&#34; id=&#34;issue-435683799-chromium&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://issues.chromium.org/issues/435683799&#34;&gt;Issue 435683799 (Chromium)&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#issue-435683799-chromium&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Impact: Memory corruption in a highly privileged GPU process&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Description: A heap-buffer-overflow in ANGLE on macOS was addressed.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;</description>
    </item>
